{
  "stem": "7938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the-- the good situation didn't take too long-- didn't last too long, because once they told us we were a small group, the other group from what I mentioned, the NKF, was going a little bit longer from that.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- they asked us-- they asked us in the morning-- they told us on the gate that we will have-- that this group, our group, will only go out for the next-- till the end of next week.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after this, we will have to come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We will have to look for another job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So of course what could we do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I started-- I asked my friend in the company, the Polish fellow, whom-- whom I gave some money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I trusted some money, I gave him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I asked him to give me, bring me back, but nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't see one penny from this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Apparently, they told me later that he-- he got drunk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He made parties with the-- with the German soldier who was the contact with the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't get-- I didn't see any money anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on the Friday, we got whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody brought some-- some food, whatever they needed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they came, and we came back to the-- to the camp",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the last day that we went out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came to the-- to the gates, and one of the soldiers went to the-- to the gate, and he registered us that we are coming back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at the same time, the gate opened and a car came out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the car was sitting the Commandant of the camp, Amon Goeth, with his chauffeur, with his Jewish chauffeur, who was on the side sitting there, probably tested the car.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
